title: Colombia's BALTHVS perform Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents BALTHVS performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 1, 2024.

Songs:
Anouk 01:07
Ojos Verdes 04:49
Johanna's Dream 11:28
Turkish Coffee 13:50

Balthazar Aguirre - Guitar
Johanna Mercuriana- Bass, Vocals
Santiago Lizcano - Drums

Host: Albina Cabrera
Audio Engineer: Jon Roberts
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Scott Holpainen, Luke Knecht & Kendall Rock
Editor: Jim Beckmann
